  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Voodoo Pin\" is a short shooting game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can shoot pins on the rotating fixed target, pay attention to avoid the pins that have already occupied their positions, and shoot into the area corresponding to the color of the pins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Insert the limited number of pins into the target successfully in each level, light the candles, then you  complete the level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259810/extras/c28316c0f82e95e05f5fbc059a80fb8d.poster.avif?t=1745773383\" width=800 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259810/extras/c28316c0f82e95e05f5fbc059a80fb8d.webm?t=1745773383\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259810/extras/c28316c0f82e95e05f5fbc059a80fb8d.mp4?t=1745773383\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features 🪡</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14 kinds of targets with different shapes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 types of shots + 2 types of pins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >21 levels to challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40 minutes of gameplay time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You may try the same level countless times.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259810/extras/25981e1cef99c6a26a1dea51b9da383f.poster.avif?t=1745773383\" width=800 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259810/extras/25981e1cef99c6a26a1dea51b9da383f.mp4?t=1745773383\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Voodoo Pin\" is a short shooting game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can shoot pins on the rotating fixed target, pay attention to avoid the pins that have already occupied their positions, and shoot into the area corresponding to the color of the pins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Insert the limited number of pins into the target successfully in each level, light the candles, then you  complete the level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259810/extras/c28316c0f82e95e05f5fbc059a80fb8d.poster.avif?t=1745773383\" width=800 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259810/extras/c28316c0f82e95e05f5fbc059a80fb8d.webm?t=1745773383\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259810/extras/c28316c0f82e95e05f5fbc059a80fb8d.mp4?t=1745773383\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features 🪡</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14 kinds of targets with different shapes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 types of shots + 2 types of pins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >21 levels to challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40 minutes of gameplay time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You may try the same level countless times.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259810/extras/25981e1cef99c6a26a1dea51b9da383f.poster.avif?t=1745773383\" width=800 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259810/extras/25981e1cef99